strings.Value: "I don't like this whole Bloom Season! What if that scoundrel we saw in the First World wants to grow another flower?"
"I... don't think that is likely to happen. Creating a second Everblooming Flower would require far too much effort."
"I agree. I prefer an honest fight â€” and I dislike the unknown. Enemies who stab you in the back, with the help of alien magic."
"It would be less amusing, the second time."
